{"tid":1401722,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家一齊比啲勇氣零售業、飲食業一齊罷工！","createTime":"2019-08-03T15:05:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T19:47:22.000Z","uid":283582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"54b6b53a54bbe18c77ae3153dcf447da014a0590","tid":1401722,"uid":283582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:05:02.000Z","msg":"見到好多post都喺度清算啲奶支嘅舖頭<br />\n罷買罷食就必然！與此同時，支持反送中嘅我地都一定要支持番佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家都唔係唔知香港零售同飲食業係幾咁有責任心，八號波黑雨都照番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我地要比佢地知道，香港人係齊上齊落，佢支持我地嘅，我地日後必定十倍奉還，令佢地有安全感，等佢地放心罷工，咁其實罷一日都沒什麼大不了啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">零售業、飲食業嘅朋友，你地放心罷工啦！你地嘅心意我地絕對會收到，我地之後一定識做！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L4PP5XH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL4PP5XH.png&h=7d42a9c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n八月五日 我會罷工！"},{"pid":"de06b316b3c79aac231b2429c73a5db383f411c5","tid":1401722,"uid":283582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:07:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"881d5a222408227cb9fe66baca03920fd79c6b74","tid":1401722,"uid":283582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:07:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"226a08707afb6f1d438d230af668b9d6bbd25d62","tid":1401722,"uid":283582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:08:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"07541450511e6db7e69351e8b9e6162cb2b36466","tid":1401722,"uid":283582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:08:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"576dfd5ae60694ab87fb3ebbd2ab35b4c3848031","tid":1401722,"uid":283582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:09:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a19aa723c6b5e57dd253c37001a40acc8d9b85a6","tid":1401722,"uid":283582,"lik